There was another judge on the other side.

122
00:07:53,380 --> 00:07:56,380
Maybe he saw a couple more mistakes than I did.

123
00:07:56,380 --> 00:07:58,380
So maybe this one would be a little bit lower.

124
00:07:58,380 --> 00:08:00,380
It might be a 5 point something.

125
00:08:00,380 --> 00:08:04,380
Another judge on the other side, they scored a little bit higher.

126
00:08:04,380 --> 00:08:07,380
So we'd get three numbers, and then we'd average that as well.

127
00:08:07,380 --> 00:08:10,380
So I hope this helped you guys.

128
00:08:10,380 --> 00:08:13,380
So make sure you enjoy your Poomsae competitions.

